=====================
Binutils Build Notes
=====================

Home: https://www.gnu.org/software/binutils/

Download: <GNU mirror>/gnu/gnu/binutils/binutils-2.27.tar.bz2

License: GPL and LGPL

Uses Autoconf and Autogen Makefile template.

for selected subdirs
  configure ...
  make
  make install

Note: we selectively configure and build just what we use, some of the
other subpackages cause problems.

Note: the binutils-lite tar file is the original tar file minus
several large directories that we don't use.  This is strictly for
space in the git repo.  The full tar file would work just as well.

Now using native (unpatched) binutils.

